{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u203bThe game allows for custom buttons, including the controller and keyboard and mouse, and the controller has vibration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u203bIf the controller does not respond, please follow the following settings: right-click the game name \u2192 Properties \u2192 Controller \u2192 Use default settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SLASHING NIGHT is an action game developed and published by YUGIKOBO, paying tribute to high-speed action games such as Devil May Cry and Bayonetta, and striving to restore their operability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gameplay: Players can quickly switch weapons in the game and perform air or ground combos. The game allows custom buttons and supports controllers and keyboards and mice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Skill system: Players must enter the skill menu to learn skills to obtain the desired abilities. Magic shields and perfect dodges can slow down the enemy's movements and provide opportunities for counterattacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat features: Use stomping on enemies, double jumps, teleportation, and air dodges to perform gorgeous air combos. Use energy to release high-damage skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is designed to provide a fast-paced combat experience, combining a rich combat system and skill learning mechanism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Magic shield and perfect dodge can slow down the enemy's movements. Take this opportunity to counterattack the enemy!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/07b_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/04_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/03_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use stepping on enemies, double jump, teleport, and air dodge to perform gorgeous aerial combos. Aerial attacks can increase the damage rate more easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/01_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consume energy to release high-damage skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/02_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Switch between different weapons and perform gorgeous combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/05_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/06_450_15fps.gif?t=1739801553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3291030?t=1739801553","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739801553","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/8d4f20301e6c7786e743efa89b990b283c219b4d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739801553","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/8d4f20301e6c7786e743efa89b990b283c219b4d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739801553","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2